      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Rare Find: Mint Condition Gem \u2014 Priced to Impress! \u2014 If you've been searching for a truly exceptional vehicle, your search ends here! This car is in outstanding mint condition \u2014 we're talking flawless interior, gleaming exterior with no visible blemishes, and mechanically spotless from top to bottom. Every system runs like a dream, and the attention to care this vehicle has received over its lifetime really shows. Whether you're a discerning daily driver or simply want the best, this is a fantastic opportunity to own a car that looks and feels brand new. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will exceed your expectations!",
      "price": 46000.0,
