    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be fully transparent so you can make an informed decision. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect heavy scratching, dents, and paint that has faded and peeled in multiple areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and a general sense of heavy use throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car has known issues that will require attention \u2014 it runs, but it is not reliable transportation without repair work. There are warning lights present on the dashboard, and the suspension feels rough and uneven. This vehicle is best suited for someone with mechanical skills looking for a project car, or a buyer who needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in repairs. We are pricing it accordingly and encourage any serious buyer to have it inspected by a mechanic before purchase.",
      "price": 6500.0,
