      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly Project Car \u2014 Priced to Move! \ud83d\udd27 Looking for an affordable set of wheels or a hands-on project? This vehicle is in poor condition and is priced accordingly \u2014 no surprises here! It has significant wear and will need some meaningful attention and repairs to get it back into reliable daily shape. That said, it's a real opportunity for a mechanically savvy buyer or someone looking for an affordable fix-up. Everything is disclosed upfront because we believe you deserve to know exactly what you're getting. If you're ready to roll up your sleeves, this could be your next project! Come take a look and decide for yourself.",
      "price": 5500.0,
